Mozambique, Portugal Sign Accord to Fight Tax Evasion, AIM Says

-- B y   F r e d   K a t e r e r e
-- 
2011-05-24T15:21:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-24/mozambique-portugal-sign-accord-to-fight-tax-evasion-aim-says.html
Mozambique and  Portugal  signed a
bilateral agreement to combat fraud and tax evasion, Agencia de
Informacao de Mocambique reported, citing the Portuguese Finance
Ministry.  Under the agreement, tax authorities will exchange
information to combat evasion and fraud by the countriesâ€™
citizens doing business in each nation, the Maputo-based  news
agency  said. Portugal has signed similar agreements with  Brazil 
and  Cape Verde , it reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
